raw_data.title: Sr. Systems Analyst
raw_data.description: Analyzes user interfaces, maintain hardware and software performance tuning, analyze workload and computer usage, maintain interfaces with outside systems, analyze downtimes, analyze proposed system modifications, upgrades and new COTS. Analyzes and develops computer systems possessing a wide range of capabilities, including numerous engineering, business and records management functions.  Develops plans for automated information systems from project inception to conclusion. Analyzes the problem and the information to be processed.
